high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the microwave on the kitchen counter.
Pick up the knife on the edge of the counter, on the left side of the microwave and salt.
Move to your right until you reach the kitchen counter between the microwave and the stove.
Cut the tomato on the counter, behind the eggs, into slices.
Move to your left until you are back in front of the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave and shut the microwave door.
Move to your right, until you are back in front of the counter between the stove and the microwave.
Pick up one of the tomato slices, on the counter, behind the eggs.
Move back over to your left, in front of the microwave.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave, in front of the knife, warm the tomato slice, then remove the tomato slice.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator with the slice of tomato.
Place the slice of tomato in the right side of the refrigerator, in front of the bowl.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm tomato slice in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn around and face the counter to the left of the microwave
Grab the knife that is to the left of the microwave
Turn right and face the counter on the right of the microwave
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices
Turn left and stop at the microwave
Put the knife into the microwave
Turn right and stop at the counter on the right of the microwave
Pick up a slice of the tomato
Turn left and stop at the microwave
Heat the tomato in the microwave and then take it out
Turn around and head to the fridge
Put the tomato in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Putting a tomato slice in the fridge

high_descs: Turn around, go towards the door, turn right and go towards the end of the counter where the microwave is.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn right, go forward, turn left at the counter to the left of the oven.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the microwave on the counter.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn right, go forward, turn left at the counter to the left of the oven.
Take a slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the microwave on the counter.
Cook the tomato in the microwave. Take the tomato from the microwave.
Turn right, go forward, turn right at the oven, go forward to the fridge.
Put the tomato in the fridge's right side in front of the bowl.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of tomato in a fridge.
